title: #92Noon! Wobby/Zimmer/Leber/Birk
description: #92Noon is LIVE from the TCO Performance Center for Vikings Mini-Camp! Wobby starts off the show to talk about the team, Vikings Head Coach Mike Zimmer continues the conversation. Ben Leber joins the show and Matt Birk makes his regular appearance all out in Eagan!
